query:
SELECT 
  id,
  productName,
  pickingOrderId,
  CASE WHEN pickingOrderId IS NULL THEN 'NULL' ELSE CONCAT('ID:', pickingOrderId) END as status
FROM pickingWaveItems
WHERE id IN (30015, 30016, 30017, 30018, 30019);
